snippet.title: Half-Life 2: THE MASKED PRISONER - Full Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Full Playthrough of the Half-Life 2 Mod - The Masked Prisoner Mod in a Single Video, Maximum Graphical Detail with NO deaths.

★★★ Please SUBSCRIBE, LIKE and SHARE ★★★ Thanks :)
